== 發行 ==
《馴龍高手2》入選了[[第67屆坎城影展|第67屆坎城影展]]的非競賽片單元，並於2014年5月15日在影展上全球首映。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|last1=Chang|first1=Justin|last2=Keslassy|first2=Elsa|title=Cannes Unveils 2014 Official Selection Lineup|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/cannes-unveils-2014-official-selection-lineup-1201158710|accessdate=2014-04-17|newspaper=Variety|date=2014-04-17|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140418083246/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/cannes-unveils-2014-official-selection-lineup-1201158710/|archivedate=2014-04-18}}</ref>後來，它被製作成[[IMAX#IMAX_3D|IMAX 3D]]版本並於2014年6月13日在包含了[[美國|美國]]等數個國家的電影院上映。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|last=Vlessing|first=Etan|title=Imax to Breathe Fire With ''How to Train Your Dragon 2'' 3D Release|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/imax-breathe-fire-how-train-698117|accessdate=2014-04-23|newspaper=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2014-04-22|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140425124441/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/imax-breathe-fire-how-train-698117|archivedate=2014-04-25}}</ref>

該片於2014年11月11日同時發行[[2D|2D]]和[[3D電影|3D]]的[[DVD|DVD]]以及[[藍光|藍光]]版本。

== 評價 ==

=== 媒體評論 ===
《馴龍高手2》在評論界中受到了媒體廣泛的好評。大多數的評價中稱讚了整部電影壯麗的視覺美感和飛行片段的動畫效果，不過對於本片的劇情，影評人褒貶不一。有人認為續集帶給人情感的共鳴極佳、甚至不遜於前作；但也有人認為其劇情的結構紊亂不明，使用了過於大膽的手法卻未能成功地突顯出一個明確的主題。根據[[爛蕃茄|爛蕃茄]]上收集的176篇評論文章，其中有161篇給出了「新鮮」的正面評價，「新鮮度」為91%，[[加權平均數|平均得分]]7.7（最高10分），該網站上對本片的共識評價中寫道：「《馴龍高手2》驚險刺激、有著使人共鳴的情感和豔美絕倫的動畫，它踏著前作成功的腳印完美地達到了一部續集應有的水準。」<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |title= How to Train Your Dragon 2 (2014) |url= http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/how_to_train_your_dragon_2/ |publisher= Flixster [[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |accessdate= 2014-06-18 |deadurl= no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140613214146/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/how_to_train_your_dragon_2/ |archivedate= 2014-06-13 }}</ref>而在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上收集的39篇評論文章中，有32篇給出好評，7篇褒貶不一，這也屬於極為正面的評價。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url= http://metacritic.com/movie/how-to-train-your-dragon-2 |title= How to Train Your Dragon 2 Reviews |publisher= [[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]] Metacritic |date=  |accessdate= 2014-06-13 |deadurl= no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140613192155/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/how-to-train-your-dragon-2 |archivedate= 2014-06-13 }}</ref>[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]進行的[[市場調查|市場調查]]顯示影迷對本片的平均評價為「A」（最好A+，最差F），其中25歲以下觀眾對其評價最高，為「A+」。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web | title = Box Office: Why Did '22 Jump Street' Win Against 'How to Train Your Dragon 2'? | date = 2014-06-16 | author = Gary Susman | url = http://news.moviefone.com/2014/06/16/box-office-22-jump-street/ | work = MovieFone.com | quote = A- for "Jump Street," A for "Dragon 2" | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140618061107/http://news.moviefone.com/2014/06/16/box-office-22-jump-street/# | archivedate = 2014-06-18 | access-date = 2014-07-29 }}</ref>

對於這部電影的正面評論多半褒獎了它的視覺效果、劇情共鳴，以及導演大膽但創新的手法使得續集不致落入窠臼。在[[第67屆坎城影展|第67屆坎城影展]]上，《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝]]》雜誌的記者彼得·迪布吉（Peter Debruge）受訪時讚賞了這部電影和它的野心：「要製作出一部四方位（男性、女性、年齡大於及小於25歲的觀眾）兼顧的巨作所帶來的壓力想必是非常龐大的。然而就像他的電影中那位臨危不亂的英雄小嗝嗝一般，《馴龍高手2》的編劇兼導演[[迪恩·戴布洛伊|迪恩·戴布洛伊]]取得了壓倒性的勝利，成功完成了[[夢工廠動畫|夢工廠動畫]]迄今為止最強大的一部續集——它為整個系列點燃了熊熊的烈火，而不是只拿著原作老調重彈。這部電影比《[[勇敢傳說|勇敢傳說]]》更加勇敢、比《[[冰雪奇緣|冰雪奇緣]]》更有趣味，帶給人情感上的滿足更是超越了許多非動畫卡通的對手。」<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |last= Debruge |first= Peter |title= Cannes Film Review: ‘How to Train Your Dragon 2’ |url= http://variety.com/2014/film/reviews/cannes-film-review-how-to-train-your-dragon-2-1201181707/ |work= [[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |accessdate= 2014-05-16 |date= 2014-05-16 |deadurl= no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140517114812/http://variety.com/2014/film/reviews/cannes-film-review-how-to-train-your-dragon-2-1201181707/ |archivedate= 2014-05-17 }}</ref>《[[紐約每日新聞|紐約每日新聞]]》的記者伊莉莎白·韦兹曼（Elizabeth Weitzman）給了這部電影5顆星中的3顆，說道：「是它大膽激烈卻堅定不移的手法給了這部電影令人意想不到的深度。」<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/movies/train-dragon-2-movie-review-article-1.1825764 |title='How to Train Your Dragon 2,' movie review |publisher=NY Daily News |date= |accessdate=2014-06-13 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140613021203/http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/movies/train-dragon-2-movie-review-article-1.1825764 |archivedate=2014-06-13 }}</ref>[[美聯社|美聯社]]記者乔赛琳·诺维克（Jocelyn Noveck）給了這部電影4顆星中的3顆，說道：「《馴龍高手2》的手法打出的並不是一張安全牌，但那也使它成為了一部罕見、不會令人感到一成不變的續集。」<ref>{{en}}{{cite news | author = Jocelyn Noveck | agency = Associated Press | url = http://www.philly.com/philly/entertainment/movies/20140610_ap_e56d9fd1b22347ac9e4e00b7e04550ee.html | title = Review: Lovely visuals, smart writing in 'Dragon' | publisher = Philly.com | date = 2012-10-22 | accessdate = 2014-06-13 | archive-url = https://archive.is/20140613211643/http://www.philly.com/philly/entertainment/movies/20140610_ap_e56d9fd1b22347ac9e4e00b7e04550ee.html | archive-date = 2014-06-13 | dead-url = no }}</ref>《[[紐約郵報|紐約郵報]]》的{{link-en|羅·盧曼尼克|Lou Lumenick}}給了這部電影4顆星中的3顆，說道：「當《馴龍高手2》裡的英雄騎在龍背上飛行時，好似整部電影都真的和他一同翱翔了。不只如此，電影中也帶給了年輕觀眾們一些有關家庭、生態和戰爭的重要課題。」<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |last=Lumenick |first=Lou |url=http://nypost.com/2014/06/11/charming-how-to-train-your-dragon-sequel-soars/ |title=Charming ‘How to Train Your Dragon’ sequel soars |publisher=Nypost.com |date= |accessdate=2014-06-13 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140616053541/http://nypost.com/2014/06/11/charming-how-to-train-your-dragon-sequel-soars/ |archivedate=2014-06-16 }}</ref>《[[娛樂周刊|娛樂周刊]]》的喬·麦戈文（Joe McGovern）給了這部電影「B」的分數，並說道：「雖然軌道還需要一些修正，但這確實是一套知道該如何飛行的電影系列。」<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |author=Joe McGovern |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20824997,00.html |title=How To Train Your Dragon 2 Review |publisher=EW.com |date= |accessdate=2014-06-13 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140615213337/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20824997,00.html |archivedate=2014-06-15 }}</ref>《[[滾石_(雜誌)|滾石]]》雜誌的[[彼得·崔維斯|彼得·崔維斯]]給了這部電影4顆星中的3顆半，說道：「《馴龍高手2》就如同當年的《[[星際大戰五部曲：帝國大反擊|帝國大反擊]]》一般，為續集提升了更高一層的想像和創新。它確實是一部同時達到顛峰卻又極具深度、且值得讓人期待的巨作。」<ref>{{en}}{{cite web | author = Peter Travers | url = http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/reviews/how-to-train-your-dragon-2-20140612 | title = 'How to Train Your Dragon 2' Movie Review | work = [[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]] | publisher = Wenner Media LLC | date = 2013-06-28 | accessdate = 2014-06-20 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170122081602/http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/reviews/how-to-train-your-dragon-2-20140612 | archivedate = 2017-01-22 }}</ref>《[[舊金山紀事報|舊金山紀事報]]》的彼得·哈特劳伯（Peter Hartlaub）給了這部電影4顆星中的3顆，說道：「兼任編劇的戴布洛伊成功地操弄了劇情中的多個故事主線，並藉著這個技巧轉換故事中角色所效忠的對象、以及探索未知的土地。」<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |author=Peter Hartlaub |url=http://www.sfgate.com/movies/article/How-to-Train-Your-Dragon-2-review-It-s-Hiccup-5547829.php |title='How to Train Your Dragon 2' review: It's Hiccup vs. tyrant |publisher=SFGate |date= |accessdate=2014-06-13 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140612193825/http://www.sfgate.com/movies/article/How-to-Train-Your-Dragon-2-review-It-s-Hiccup-5547829.php |archivedate=2014-06-12 }}</ref> 《[[多倫多星報|多倫多星報]]》的彼得·霍韋爾（Peter Howell）給了這部電影4顆星中的3顆，說道：「《馴龍高手2》中來自《[[星際大戰|星際大戰]]》和《[[冰與火之歌：權力遊戲|權力遊戲]]》的靈感、以及它本身故事敘述的風格兩者等量地融合後，成為了一部為整個系列點燃了烈火的續集。」<ref>{{en}}{{cite web | author = Peter Howell | url = http://www.thestar.com/entertainment/movies/2014/06/12/how_to_train_your_dragon_sequel_breathes_fire_review.html | title = How to Train Your Dragon sequel breathes fire: review | work = Toronto Star | date = 2014-06-12 | accessdate = 2014-06-20 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140617181917/http://www.thestar.com/entertainment/movies/2014/06/12/how_to_train_your_dragon_sequel_breathes_fire_review.html | archivedate = 2014-06-17 }}</ref>《[[今日美國|今日美國]]》的克勞迪亞·普伊格（Claudia Puig）給了這部電影4顆星中的3顆，說道：「幾近原作般的熱血沸騰，《馴龍高手2》巧妙地避免了一部無趣、公式化的續集。」<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2014/06/11/how-to-train-your-dragon-2-review/9649005/ |title='Dragon' breathes fire into deeper, darker sequel |publisher=Usatoday.com |date=2013-12-20 |accessdate=2014-06-13 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140613053026/http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2014/06/11/how-to-train-your-dragon-2-review/9649005/ |archivedate=2014-06-13 }}</ref>《[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]》的史蒂芬妮·梅里（Stephanie Merry）給了這部電影4顆星中的3顆半，說道：「這可能是第一次也是最後一次任何人這麼說，但既然《馴龍高手2》這麼棒，那麼為何要在第3集或是第4集就停手呢？」<ref>{{en}}{{cite web | author = Stephanie Merry | url = http://www.washingtonpost.com/goingoutguide/movies/how-to-train-your-dragon-2-movie-review/2014/06/11/9a77638c-efdd-11e3-914c-1fbd0614e2d4_story.html | title = ‘How to Train Your Dragon 2’ movie review | publisher = Nash Holdings LLC | work = [[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]] | date = 2014-06-12 | accessdate = 2014-06-13 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140613052858/http://www.washingtonpost.com/goingoutguide/movies/how-to-train-your-dragon-2-movie-review/2014/06/11/9a77638c-efdd-11e3-914c-1fbd0614e2d4_story.html | archivedate = 2014-06-13 }}</ref>《[[西雅圖時報|西雅圖時報]]》的莫伊拉·麥當勞（Moira MacDonald）給了這部電影4顆星中的3顆半，說道：「前作的影迷們，不論老幼都將排隊等著看這部充滿了風趣的電影，為的是其中創造性十足的角色和激動人心的視覺效果——還有欣賞它們所帶來單純的樂趣。」<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |last=Macdonald |first=Moira |url=http://seattletimes.com/html/movies/2023829555_howtotrainxml.html |title=‘How to Train Your Dragon 2’ soars with wit, thrilling visuals |publisher=The Seattle Times |date= |accessdate=2014-06-13 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140715012856/http://seattletimes.com/html/movies/2023829555_howtotrainxml.html |archivedate=2014-07-15 }}</ref>《[[環球郵報|環球郵報]]》的約翰·森姆利（John Semley）給了這部電影4顆星的滿分，說道：「它不只了教導孩子們該如何思考他們即將要跨進的世界，而是一部同時鼓勵了他們為自己而思考的罕見電影。」<ref>{{en}}{{cite news |author=John Semley |url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/arts/film/film-reviews/burn-baby-burn/article19146401/ |title=How to Train Your Dragon 2: A rare film that teaches kids to think for themselves |publisher=The Globe and Mail |date= |accessdate=2014-06-13 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140708203307/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/arts/film/film-reviews/burn-baby-burn/article19146401/ |archivedate=2014-07-08 }}</ref>《[[芝加哥太陽報|芝加哥太陽報]]》的比爾·茲維克（Bill Zwecker）也給了這部電影4顆星的滿分，說道：「本片在電影魅力、動畫製作技巧、聰明的故事架構以及幽默的台詞編纂等方面不僅達到了前作的水準，我想它甚至還有過之而無不及。」<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.suntimes.com/entertainment/movies/28000422-421/how-to-train-your-dragon-2-even-better-than-the-first.html |title=‘How to Train Your Dragon 2’: Even better than the first |publisher=Suntimes.com |date= |accessdate=2014-06-14 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140617071343/http://www.suntimes.com/entertainment/movies/28000422-421/how-to-train-your-dragon-2-even-better-than-the-first.html |archivedate=2014-06-17 }}</ref>[[全國公共廣播電台|全國公共廣播電台]]的鮑伯·蒙德羅（Bob Mondello）給了這部電影10分中的8.5分，說道：「很明顯地，導演戴布洛伊從《星際大戰》系列的前三部作品中擷取了靈感——這對替好萊塢一個細膩的動畫系列帶進一些新生命、甚至是一點火花來說，是個不錯的榜樣。」<ref>{{en}}{{cite web | author = Bob Mondello | url = http://www.npr.org/2014/06/13/321663008/its-a-summer-sequel-spectacular-with-dragon-and-jump-street | title = It's A Summer Sequel Spectacular With 'Dragon' And 'Jump Street' | publisher = NPR | date =  | accessdate = 2014-06-14 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140614005646/http://www.npr.org/2014/06/13/321663008/its-a-summer-sequel-spectacular-with-dragon-and-jump-street | archivedate = 2014-06-14 }}</ref>

相對地，負評則多半認為電影的劇情安排太過花俏卻未能夠統合，也有人認為電影中主角外的其他角色未被重視而顯遺憾。《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》的史蒂芬·霍登（Stephen Holden）給了這部電影5顆星中的2顆半，說道：「整個故事原本還看來有些名堂，直到最後難以避免的光明與黑暗勢力大戰場景的出現而被迫驟停。」<ref>{{en}}{{cite news | author = Stephen Holden | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2014/06/13/movies/in-how-to-train-your-dragon-2-war-and-peace-and-beasties.html | title = In ‘How to Train Your Dragon 2,’ War and Peace and Beasties | publisher = The New York Times | date = 2014-06-13 | accessdate = 2014-06-13 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140613050301/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/06/13/movies/in-how-to-train-your-dragon-2-war-and-peace-and-beasties.html | archivedate = 2014-06-13 }}</ref>《{{link-en|明星纪事报|The Star-Ledger}}》的史蒂芬·惠迪（Stephen Whitty）給了這部電影4顆星中的2顆半，說道：「這是個完全不必要的續集，除了對那些會計師來說。而甚至已經有了下一部的計畫。」<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |author= Stephen Whitty |work= The Star-Ledger |url= http://www.nj.com/entertainment/index.ssf/2014/06/how_to_train_your_dragon_2_review_the_sequel_that_fell_to_earth.html |title= 'How to Train Your Dragon 2' review: The sequel that fell to earth |publisher= NJ.com |date=  |accessdate= 2014-06-13 |deadurl= no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140709135850/http://www.nj.com/entertainment/index.ssf/2014/06/how_to_train_your_dragon_2_review_the_sequel_that_fell_to_earth.html |archivedate= 2014-07-09 }}</ref>[[The_Wrap|The Wrap]]網站上的姜寅求（Inkoo Kang）給了這部電影褒貶不一的評價，說道：「這部電影雖然沒什麼好感受的，但至少有很多可看的。托戴布洛伊和他高超的3D導演技術的福，我們快速劃過天際、在龍的尾巴上滑翔，甚至差一點點就穿不過那小小的縫隙。不過，這些體驗都只像是在搭乘一座很棒的雲霄飛車一般，沒有任何意義。」<ref>{{en}}{{cite web | author = Inkoo Kang | url = http://www.thewrap.com/how-to-train-your-dragon-2-review-cate-blanchett-jay-baruchel-america-ferrera/ | title = 'How to Train Your Dragon 2' Review: Something Gets Lost in the Leap from Romp to Epic | publisher = TheWrap | date =  | accessdate = 2014-06-14 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140615032156/http://www.thewrap.com/how-to-train-your-dragon-2-review-cate-blanchett-jay-baruchel-america-ferrera/ | archivedate = 2014-06-15 }}</ref>《[[影音俱樂部|影音俱樂部]]》的一篇評論中給了這部電影「B-」的分數，並寫道：「本作不只有了更多的龍，它還多了更多的角色、更多的劇情和更多的所有東西。換來的代價就是，原作所具有的魅力在續集中便稍顯不足，可說是因亟欲擴張系列而急就章所帶來的後果。」<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |author= A.A. Dowd |url= http://www.avclub.com/review/how-train-your-dragon-2-has-more-dragons-less-soul-205664 |title= How To Train Your Dragon 2 has more dragons, less soul than its predecessor |publisher= Avclub.com |date=  |accessdate= 2014-06-14 |deadurl= no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140614024732/http://www.avclub.com/review/how-train-your-dragon-2-has-more-dragons-less-soul-205664 |archivedate= 2014-06-14 }}</ref>《{{link-en|Cinefantastique|Cinefantastique}}》雜誌的史蒂芬·白德羅斯基（Steve Biodrowski）只給了這部電影5顆星中的1顆，說道：「編劇兼導演迪恩·戴布洛伊丟了三四個故事的想法到整個劇本中卻沒有辦法拿定主意該如何處理，導致它們在一些奇怪的場合中相交；就好像許多車輛正穿越一個繁忙的路口，然而誰也不讓誰，結果就是沒有人能夠快速地通過。」<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |author= Steve Biodrowski |url= http://cinefantastiqueonline.com/2014/06/how-to-train-your-dragon-2-review/ |title= How to Train Your Dragon 2 review |publisher= Cinefantastique |date= 2014-06-19 |accessdate= 2014-07-26 |deadurl= no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140625124647/http://cinefantastiqueonline.com/2014/06/how-to-train-your-dragon-2-review/ |archivedate= 2014-06-25 }}</ref>《{{link-en|天主教國民周刊|National Catholic Register}}》的史蒂芬·D·葛雷丹尼斯（Steven D. Greydanus）給了這部電影「C+」的分數，說道：「和《[[冰原歷險記|冰原歷險記]]》的續集一般，續集中的劇情主線可能會不同於原作，而部分的角色也可能因此而不再出現。不過以這部電影來說，在前作中所鑄造的核心角色以及他們之間的關係則已經定型了。」<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |author= Steven D. Greydanus |url= http://www.ncregister.com/daily-news/sdg-reviews-how-to-train-your-dragon-2 |title= SDG Reviews ‘How to Train Your Dragon 2’ |publisher= National Catholic Register |date= 2014-06-13 |accessdate= 2014-07-26 |deadurl= no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140716005504/http://www.ncregister.com/daily-news/sdg-reviews-how-to-train-your-dragon-2 |archivedate= 2014-07-16 }}</ref>[[澳洲|澳洲]]電視節目《{{link-en|上映電影|At the Movies (Australian TV series)}}》的主持人{{link-en|瑪格麗特·彭慕蘭|Margaret Pomeranz}}以及{{link-en|大衛·斯特拉頓|David Stratton}}也給了這部電影負評，其中瑪格麗特說道：「我覺得這就是它不對勁的地方。電影裡小角色的特色根本完全沒有浮現。我得要很花力氣才能夠分辨出他們到底誰是誰。」<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |author= Margaret Pomeranz |url= http://www.abc.net.au/atthemovies/txt/s4026182.htm |title= How to Train Your Dragon 2 |publisher= At the Movies |date= 2014-06-24 |accessdate= 2014-07-26 |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140716212516/http://www.abc.net.au/atthemovies/txt/s4026182.htm |archivedate= 2014-07-16 }}</ref>

=== 票房收入 ===
至2014年7月10日為止，《馴龍高手2》獲得了在北美地區約1.55億、其它地區約1.97億、總和約3.53億美元的票房收入。<ref name="BOM" />在[[美國|美國]]國內，本作於上映首日即達到了1850萬美元的票房收入<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url= http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2014/06/14/box-office-22-jump-street-nabs-25m-how-to-train-your-dragon-2-nabs-18-5m-on-friday/ |title= Friday Box Office: '22 Jump Street' - $25M, 'How To Train Your Dragon 2' - $18.5M |publisher= [[Forbes|Forbes]] |date= 2014-05-28 |accessdate= 2014-06-14 |deadurl= no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140616005815/http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2014/06/14/box-office-22-jump-street-nabs-25m-how-to-train-your-dragon-2-nabs-18-5m-on-friday/ |archivedate= 2014-06-16 }}</ref>，並在上映後的首個周末以約4945萬美元的成績列居第二名，落後於《[[龍虎少年隊2|龍虎少年隊2]]》。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url= http://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/chart/?yr=2014&wknd=24&p=.htm |title= Weekend Box Office Results for June 13-15, 2014 |work= [[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] |publisher= Internet Movie Database |date=  |accessdate= 2014-06-16 |deadurl= no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140618083655/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/chart/?yr=2014&wknd=24&p=.htm |archivedate= 2014-06-18 }}</ref>到第二個周末時，電影再增加了約2472萬美元的收入，並退後一名位居第三<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/chart/?yr=2014&wknd=25&p=.htm |title=Weekend Box Office Results for June 20-22, 2014 |publisher=Box Office Mojo |date= |accessdate=2014-06-24 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140625071654/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/chart/?yr=2014&wknd=25&p=.htm |archivedate=2014-06-25 }}</ref>；到第三個周末時，電影再增加了約1323萬美元的收入，仍然位居第三<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/chart/?yr=2014&wknd=26&p=.htm |title=Weekend Box Office Results for June 27-29, 2014 |publisher=Box Office Mojo |date=2014-03-07 |accessdate=2014-07-04 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140705025009/http://boxofficemojo.com/weekend/chart/?yr=2014&wknd=26&p=.htm |archivedate=2014-07-05 }}</ref>；直到第四個周末，電影才退後兩名位居第五，並再增加了896萬美元的收入。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/chart/?yr=2014&wknd=27&p=.htm |title=Weekend Box Office Results for July 4-6, 2014 |publisher=Box Office Mojo |date= |accessdate=2014-07-13 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140713052755/http://boxofficemojo.com/weekend/chart/?yr=2014&wknd=27&p=.htm |archivedate=2014-07-13 }}</ref>

