== 電子遊戲 ==
2014年6月，發行商小軌道（Little Orbit）發布了一款和電影同名的[[電子遊戲|電子遊戲]]。<ref name="PRNLittleOrbit" />該遊戲由{{link-en|Torus Games|Torus Games}}開發，並適用於[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]、[[任天堂3DS|任天堂3DS]]、[[Wii|Wii]]、[[Wii_U|Wii U]]和[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]等平台。<ref name="PRNLittleOrbit" />遊戲中，玩家可以選擇不同的角色和坐騎，進入馴龍飛行學院參與各種訓練課程、挑戰或是比賽。<ref name="PRNLittleOrbit">{{en}}{{cite press release|title=Little Orbit to Publish ''How to Train Your Dragon 2'' video games based on the upcoming film from DreamWorks Animation|url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/little-orbit-to-publish-how-to-train-your-dragon-2-video-games-based-on-the-upcoming-film-from-dreamworks-animation-250791401.html|publisher=PR Newswire|accessdate=2014-03-26|author=Little Orbit|date=2014-03-18|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140323044634/http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/little-orbit-to-publish-how-to-train-your-dragon-2-video-games-based-on-the-upcoming-film-from-dreamworks-animation-250791401.html|archivedate=2014-03-23}}</ref>

遊戲在發行之後受到了不少負評，多半批評其粗劣的畫面、無趣的飛行模式和遊戲中不斷重複卻又毫無新意的挑戰。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |last=Gill |first=Sam |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/gadgets-and-tech/gaming/how-to-train-your-dragon-2-video-game-review-a-return-to-the-bad-old-days-of-awful-movie-tieins-9575697.html |title=How To Train Your Dragon 2 video game review: a return to the bad old days of awful movie tie-ins |publisher=The Independent |date=2014-07-09 |accessdate=2014-07-28 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714105539/http://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/gadgets-and-tech/gaming/how-to-train-your-dragon-2-video-game-review-a-return-to-the-bad-old-days-of-awful-movie-tieins-9575697.html |archivedate=2014-07-14 }}</ref>

